text: Britain's Next Top Model, Cycle 5 is the fifth season of Britain's Next Top Model. This cycle includes 13 contestants. The winner 19-year-old was Mecia Simson from Plymouth, England. ==Contestants== (ages stated are at time of contest) Contestant Age Hometown Outcome Lisa-Ann Hillman 20 Newquay, England 13th Lauren Annaliese Dayes 22 London, England 7th Daisy Payne 22 London, England 6th Viola Szekely 18 Surrey, England 5th Ashley Brown 20 Livingston, Scotland 4th Jade McSorley 20 Middlesbrough, England 3rd Sophie Sumner 18 Oxford, England Runner-up Mecia Simson 19 Plymouth, England Winner ==Prizes== * A modeling contract with Models 1 * A campaign with Max Factor * A spread & cover in Company Magazine
